## 📦 Installation

**The ✨Fast Way✨ (pip)**

```bash
pip install obscuratee
```

Once installed, summon the fella:

```bash
obscuratee
```

~~Activate Vibe Mode™~~

```bash
 ̶o̶b̶s̶c̶u̶r̶a̶t̶e̶e̶ ̶-̶-̶v̶i̶b̶e̶
```

A̴̟̿c̶̖͗t̵̙̂ḭ̷͂v̵̝̈́à̶̦t̴̪͗e̶̢̋ C̴̗͐u̷̳̕r̴̓͜ş̸̔e̸̩̒ M̵͍͝o̵̜̅d̴̰̀ȇ̶͙™

```bash
obscuratee --curse
```

Use Legacy Mode (classic ASCII manatee):

```bash
obscuratee --legacy
```
